cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR 

The paper deals with the integration of textual and visual information, which suggests that it could belong to the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL) and computer vision (cs.CV). The use of modeling techniques such as PCA, CCA, and R-CCA suggests that it could also belong to the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the evaluation of the proposed method on semantic benchmarks suggests that it could also belong to the category of information retrieval (cs.IR).
